Company Summary


When considering the development new residential or commercial property, contact Wood-Ridge, NJ architect Thomas J. Mesuk. By providing designs that are both functional and aesthetically pleasing, we have set the bar for both residential and commercial architectural designs across the country. From new custom homes to complete office complexes, our team will design a space that fits your needs and budget. We offer site and building analysis, feasibility studies, energy code compliance reviews, major renovations along with construction administration. If you are looking for a firm to best represent your design ideas, call Thomas J. Musek, LLC to begin your design today.









